Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「命运相连的两人的小指被红线连系在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自古以来有着这样的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的红线又与哪里的谁相连在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,practe biginar ardescat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映夕映真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,practe biginar ardescat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么事可以一朝一夕办成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马也不是一天建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真想尽快掌握魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最近在图书馆岛探险时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在书架最里面发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…魔法书？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不会就是命运的红线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  这是能知道红线那边是谁的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想马上学会这个魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一来  就能知道我命运中的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  我们俩都还只是初学者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么难的咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人都有擅长和不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许对我而言比其他人更不费吹灰之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想知道命运的另一半是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据这本书上的记载
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎只要以最真实的感受默念所想的那个人即可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是涅吉老师…希望是涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,practe biginar filum ostrinus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,practe biginar filum ostrinus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是涅吉老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红线延伸向远方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Negima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  不是的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是将命运的红线视觉化的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是将人与人用红线连结起来的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉突然被拽跑了  我还以为发生什么事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为红线所连接…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说来…  我和涅吉老师属于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,命运的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这怎么行…好为难…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有做好心理准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请别担心  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是晚会上用来调节气氛的小魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了晚上就会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着那么麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直接剪断它怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很碍事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一挂到什么可就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用做到那个程度也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要小心一点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡…卡莫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险啊  差点又有一个新的趣味觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是剪断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  拜托了  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剪不断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  无意中系上的这根红线却意外地结实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜荣幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法  不过幸好今天是假日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在红线消失之前  就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以一直和涅吉老师待在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在这儿呀  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家提议一起去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡？
