Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻帆良温泉疗养胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻帆良温泉疗养胜地？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（近日预定开放  Coming Soon! ）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  作为它的落成纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想让涅吉老师最先光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就在正式开业之前  特别对本班开放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  请大家尽情地享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉很讨厌洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…这样的我还是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈…  所以很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和涅吉老师一起洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很大规模呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错嘛  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春…春奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候和涅吉老师发展为手牵手走路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是你想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为线太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,线…  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香同学  没有魔力的人似乎是看不见这根红线的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,V
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是个稀奇的魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可无法赞同这种没有完全掌握就随便使用的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就走了呢  等等啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是危险的魔法的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么认真嘛  不也很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像刑事侦探片一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刑事侦探片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs49.5}嫌疑犯  涅吉{\r}\N涅吉·斯普林菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fs49.5}警官  和香  (俗称  书店){\r}\N宫琦  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真叫人心跳加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩也来连连看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那样…  大小姐  请别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以  请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们俩去那边好好休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  好好休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  因为这样没办法换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学你们就别管我们  尽情地享受温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算就这样来为你讨厌洗澡这件事开脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会  你误会了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那件破T恤即使撕破了也没什么好可惜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不介意  可和香同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没得商量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  书店妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师  宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  请别在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…啊  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个傻瓜涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服的温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美国哪个州有很多喜欢洗澡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  因为叫作「入浴」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为「洗澡」  所以是佛罗里达～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我如果回答是佛罗里达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是「入浴」  所以是纽约～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这人就是这副德行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说气泡温泉可以促进血液循环  加速新陈代谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对皮肤也很有好处  扑露扑露好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,气泡温泉还有一个特别先进的功效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是放屁也不会暴露哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是放屁也不会暴露…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开个玩笑是也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真名  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  这枪可以在水中使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水汞推进式霰弹捕鱼枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是大白鲨也同样一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浴池里没有鲨鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现这玩意掉在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我正在找它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了  美空？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（要参照Negima春）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又把它带来了吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗得真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我又复活了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  你要复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,独家新闻独家新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿照相机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会回来  等会再复活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是那个意思啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  我来帮你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么可以  大小姐  不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由我来给大小姐擦背才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那好吧  就拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和涅吉老师一起洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这根红线能够就这样一直连着该有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裹着浴巾泡澡  是违反礼节的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…在涅吉老师的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这又不是TV动画！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快把多余的东西拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经洗好了洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下  和香…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  好不容易想凭借色诱事件使两人的关系更进一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈实在是太胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  反正我也洗得快差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去那边喝点果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没好好洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就坐在那儿别动  让我给你好好洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  明日菜同学  我自己能洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎  明明自己连头发都洗不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了单手还绑着红线呢  这样要怎么洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  请别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算这样逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来趟这么好的浴池不容易  我一定要给你彻底洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叶加濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早就料到会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我用了两周的时间制造出这台超级便利入浴机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快来体验一下触手君MK-V的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标捕捉  清洗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底为他清洗干净！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞…搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  我指的是涅吉不是我自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菜单1  去除衣物开始按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好痒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
