Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Give  Give  Give  Give up～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来疲劳就从身体内部烟消云散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:06.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,痛～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是美容保养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如说是关节技？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超  那个手臂的姿势不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样  只要2秒就能搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…杀了她怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,借用了厨房做的  水果鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常适合在洗完澡以后饮用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清淡美妙清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有利于补充因出汗而流失的水分和维他命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么呢  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易与老师的关系有了一定的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去可以两人独处的地方可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人独处…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我知道个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下  春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪…哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Happy Banana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  看招  接着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜者  扎吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  为什么我会输在乒乓球上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扎吉真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这和杂技技巧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  还有没有其她对战者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确信自己能够战胜扎吉的挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  意外地能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶茶丸  给她点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛开始
