Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太习惯这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经  再也无法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不该让小孩洗桑拿浴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卫生兵
