Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  和香同学早上好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天气可真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情不错  我来摸摸你的头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别跟我客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那我就恭敬不如从命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊  对不起  对不起  对不起
