Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  雪广观光集团是绝对不会出这种差错的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师  我这里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.25,0:24:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.00,0:24:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的红线一定仍然连接着
