Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.82,0:24:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
